snippet.title: Exp Parasite
snippet.description:
Exp Parasite
A hardcore 2D arcade game for old-school players. The user controls an experimental parasite that infects different mechanisms, overcomes countless obstacles, and fights powerful bosses to achieve goals set by an unknown puppeteer.
